snippet: Jordan Spieth, the world’s No. 1-ranked player, finished as runner-up at the Singapore Open on Monday after Song Young-han held on to beat the fast-finishing Spieth by a stroke.
abstract: Song Young-han wins Singapore Open golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth, the world’s No. 1-ranked player, finished as runner-up at the Singapore Open on Monday after Song Young-han held on to beat the fast-finishing Spieth by a stroke.
